29
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,439
The Hour of the Rabbit.

30
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,039
But why would he

31
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:50,520
die in my room?

32
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:52,800
That is a question for you.

33
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,400
Were you not in your room last night?

34
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,639
Recently, I...

35
